name: Infinite Phil (Hartman/Donahue)
description:
2004; 12 second MP4 loop; originally created for The Infinite Fill Group Show at Foxy Production curated by Cory and Jamie Arcangel. 

"Phil Hartman playing the talk-show host Phil Donahue, endlessly shaking his head in a [12]-second loop from some long-ago ''Saturday Night Live'' segment"
